item.title: 关于我
item.description: Hi, I’m Davy, an undergraduate student studying Electronic Information Engineering at Hohai University(HHU), expected to graduate in 2022. HHU BEng(EIE) 2018 👉 CUHK MSc(EE) 2022 Fall I am currently learning Computer Science through self-study, and I am passionate about being a software developer in the future. Recently, I am facinated by Go and back-end technologies, and I would like to write more blogs about these topic
